{"tid":1777622,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"救手足 勿忘桂民海案 瑞典前駐華大使涉擅自就「桂民海事件」與中方談判，正式被起訴","createTime":"2019-12-10T10:41:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-10T14:21:17.000Z","uid":165683,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"5a3848560cf5c1ebe36a0311620c99206ce2ff07","tid":1777622,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T10:41:04.000Z","msg":"瑞典前駐華大使涉擅自就「桂民海事件」與中方談判，面臨最高監禁十年<br />\n瑞典前駐華大使林戴安（Anna Lindstedt）涉嫌擅自安排香港「銅鑼灣書店」前股東桂民海的女兒 Angela 與兩名中國「商人」會面，被瑞典檢察部門控以「與外國勢力談判期間獨斷獨行罪」，面臨最高監禁十年。<br />\n<br />\n瑞典檢察部門於當地週一（9日）指出，林戴安是瑞典近代首名被控「與外國勢力談判期間獨斷獨行罪」的外交官。檢察部門解釋，林戴安擔任瑞典外交人員期間，必須按照外交部及政府的指引行事，惟林戴安在本案中的行為超出職權範圍，必須負上刑事責任。由於司法程序展開，外交部此前對林戴安展開的內部調查已經暫停。<br />\n<br />\n《晚報：瑞典前駐華大使涉擅自就「桂民海事件」與中方談判，正式被起訴》 <a href=\"https://theinitium.com/article/20191210-evening-brief/?utm_medium=copy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftheinitium.com%2Farticle%2F20191210-evening-brief%2F%3Futm_medium%3Dcopy&d=%2BaoNGjxKkOyNIKnkVXg3cbccVloK1XwbfTGMhSGe0oU%3D&h=42430e9c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://theinitium.com/article/20191210-evening-brief/?utm_medium=copy</a> <br />\n&copy; 端傳媒 Initium Media"},{"pid":"426ff294c38914feaade8f22f1f878059fbeb2f7","tid":1777622,"uid":249263,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T10:41:49.000Z","msg":"（Twitter戰線）歐盟Magnitsky Act有重要進程<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1776924\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1776924</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">twitter要人: 歐盟今日啟動Magnitsky Act 立法程序，詳細議會仲要傾，但歐洲戰線開啟左啦，快啲入去講邊個國家的人最需要被裁裁啦！！</span><span style=\"color: orange;\"><br />\n幫手入去retweet同推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\nTwitter組24小時keep住更新<br />\n幫手retweet<br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=%2BaoNGjxKkOyNIKnkVXg3cbccVloK1XwbfTGMhSGe0oU%3D&h=7bb6a172\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打 /task 攞任務"},{"pid":"4721fb6d82d819ad4ce93aaa2cfab991786e1e87","tid":1777622,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T10:43:14.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c860cb9d04355ffe9424c1c852ee2d4ab201e161","tid":1777622,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T10:44:44.000Z","msg":"投共可恥"},{"pid":"06ca2e2c1eaeace99cb8e674e14922cc6e533b50","tid":1777622,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T10:45:26.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">尋找黑警性暴力證人/受害者，協助國際遊說</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2640629789347426&amp;id=124616407615456\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2640629789347426%26id%3D124616407615456&d=%2BaoNGjxKkOyNIKnkVXg3cbccVloK1XwbfTGMhSGe0oU%3D&h=b608cff3\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2640629789347426&amp;id=124616407615456</a><br />\n<br />\nPost：<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eDEkrT\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eDEkrT</a><br />\n<br />\n//平等機會婦女聯席發言人區美寶稱，3個組織11月初共同發起控訴警察性暴力的國際聯署，截至本月7日收集到21國共85個團體聯署支持。為了向聯合國專家展開更有力游說，3個組織呼籲受害者主動聯絡他們並接受訪談，強調會保密。//<br />\n<br />\n我們現正收集抗爭者在抗爭期間／被捕後遭受警察性暴力對待的資料，作以下用途：<br />\n1. 協助受害人可以完整保留該事件之紀錄<br />\n2. 整理資料並製成 #ProtestToo 實錄，以作追究之用<br />\n3. 收集國際聯署（進行中），結合個案提交聯合國，爭取國際間關注及支持<br />\n4. 要求香港政府獨立、公正地徹查「反送中運動」發生的性暴力<br />\n<br />\n*個人資料及通訊紀錄在實錄完成後可按受訪者意願全部銷毀<br />\n詳情及相關安排請聯絡Tg @protesttoo"},{"pid":"070bcaf5337cda4361a866d3def8ea4465aa8e1f","tid":1777622,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T10:48:08.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"31b7c0dce9bbf4769e3e497214d99e8f57f4f13f","tid":1777622,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T10:49:49